    <section class="slideshow">
      <div  data-aos="fade-up">
        <ul id="throwlist">
            <li class="throwli">
               <img class="successphoto"  src="photos\dog.jpg"> </a></li>
            <li class="throwli"><h4 style="font-size: 22px;">From Stray to Family:</h4><p>
                Abandoned and alone, a stray puppy named Jasper roamed the streets until a caring individual rescued her. Today, Jasper thrives in a loving home, reminding us that every pet deserves a chance at happiness.</p></li>
